cast
Discworld player help
cast

Name
.SI 5
cast - Spell casting
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
cast <spell> [target]
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Cast is used when you want to cast a spell that you have learnt in your travels
and adventures.  Most spells are the rewards of quests.  You must type cast
followed by the spell you wish to cast followed by any information that is
appropriate to the spell.  Eg a target.
.EP

Example
.SI 5
> cast light
The world lights up as you cast your spell.
> cast heal on khaos
Khaos looks like she really liked that.
.EI

See also
.SI 5
spells, kill
.EI
